We got ready with @tatigabrielle as she headed to the @toryburch Fall/Winter 2023 show at #NYFW. See her “goddess, ethereal fairy” look come to life in the full video at the link in our bio.

director: @jessiejolles
cinematographer: @johnroberthurley
senior video producer: @stephrmro
video editor: @dannijuhl

NYFW Fall/Winter 2023 Photo Dump

———————————————

Only my second fashion week and i was over the moon. thank you to all the designers who invited me @toryburch , @hellessy , @adeam , @viviennetam . it was an honor and absolute friggin pleasure to rock all of your clothes. 

And very special thank you to my NY team for making me look fly af every time i stepped out of a car lol ( i still can’t get over the crowd “woooaaah” when i stepped out for the @toryburch show teehee)

makeup: @laurelcharleston 
hair: @ivainsane 
styling: @jeanalina 

and much love to @sublimajewelry for the beautiful jewelry i got to wear all week! 

Man, what a week… 🥹🤍
#NYFW2023 #GRATEFULAF 

[p.s. if i missed any photographers please tag them bc i’m hella grateful for them too]

Quel rêve 🥰

Merci beaucoup @Balmain for making my first #PFW everything I could have asked for and more. Still reeling from it all.

Félicitations pour une autre collection incroyable @olivier_rousteing. Ce fut un honneur et un rêve de vous rencontrer. Merci de me recevoir. 🙏🏽 🤍

Until the next time, Paree 💋🇫🇷
